{\an8}<i>FEMALE VOICE:</i>
<i>Turn right in 50 meters.</i>

26
00:01:37,722 --> 00:01:38,932
{\an8}Oh, meters?

27
00:01:39,015 --> 00:01:42,015
{\an8}Dad, a meter is three inches
longer than a yard,

28
00:01:42,102 --> 00:01:42,852
{\an8}which is 36 inches,

29
00:01:42,936 --> 00:01:45,936
{\an8}so 50 divided by 39
times 36 equals...

30
