290
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,530
would've been considered
innocent, but in today's

291
00:12:56,609 --> 00:12:58,899
overly-litigious society

292
00:12:58,986 --> 00:13:01,776
has been blown completely
out of proportion.

293
00:13:01,864 --> 00:13:03,784
