308
00:13:36,524 --> 00:13:38,364
that guy couldn't fool anybody.

309
00:13:38,442 --> 00:13:40,152
Shut up, fatso.

310
00:13:40,236 --> 00:13:42,446
-Why you little... (grunting)
-(choking)

311
00:13:42,530 --> 00:13:44,320
