they find out about us.

404
00:17:35,471 --> 00:17:37,181
What do you mean "us"?

405
00:17:37,264 --> 00:17:40,524
Well, like, uh,
a-aren't you my girlfriend now?

406
00:17:40,601 --> 00:17:42,101
Oh, you mean,
like you own me?

407
00:17:42,186 --> 00:17:43,396
I'm sorry.

408
00:17:43,479 --> 00:17:45,859
Ugh! You're always
apologizing.

409
00:17:45,939 --> 00:17:47,269
Just tell me
what you want!

410
00:17:47,357 --> 00:17:48,937
You should <i>know</i>
what I want!

411
00:17:49,026 --> 00:17:52,196
I want you to act the same
way two days in a row! Ugh!

412
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:54,909
I'm not gonna let
you hurt me anymore.

413
00:17:54,990 --> 00:17:55,910
(screams, thuds)

414
00:17:57,076 --> 00:17:58,736
(crying):
He's dead!

415
00:17:58,827 --> 00:18:01,157
I love him!

416
00:18:01,246 --> 00:18:02,616
(breathing loudly)

417
00:18:02,706 --> 00:18:03,866
Oh, he's breathing.

418
00:18:03,957 --> 00:18:05,707
Loser.

419
00:18:13,050 --> 00:18:14,590
He's stopped breathin'!

420
00:18:14,676 --> 00:18:16,136
Who knows gob-to-gob?

421
00:18:16,678 --> 00:18:19,178
